features.text: Virtual Lapidary / Trash Collector in Reality

105COLLECTIVE IS A GROUP OF UK-BASED ARTISTS BRINGING THEIR WORK TO THE DIGITAL, VR, AND CRYPTO SPACES. THE GROUP CONVENED IN MARCH 2020 DURING THE FIRST WEEKS OF THE COVID-19 GLOBAL PANDEMIC, SEEKING WAYS TO SHARE ART IN A FORMAT ACCESSIBLE TO ALL AUDIENCES ON NOVEL SHARED-REALITY FORMATS, WHILE SIMULTANEOUSLY ALLOWING FOR THE PROSPECT OF LONG-TERM ISOLATION DUE TO SOCIAL DISTANCING .
